# Stub files accidentally created by stray Windows redirections.
# `>>npm install` typed in cmd creates a 0-byte "npm" file (stdout
# redirected) and runs whatever resolves as "install" — same for git.
# Ignoring these names entirely so they can never accidentally land
# in the repo again. Real npm and git are external commands, never
# files in this repo.
/npm
/git
